fields.title: Memrise
fields.description: This is my favorite resource for practicing Mandarin vocabulary and characters. The application will keep track of your progress and implement a spaced-repetition review cycle to help you retain what you've learned over time. There are also many other courses on a variety of subjects available, and you can create your own.
